  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Yemen</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Specific Goals: 1.Build the capacity of activists and media to monitor and document cases of torture. 2.Documentation of the history of torture at the national level before and after the unification of the North and South  in 1990 till now in order to shed light on cases  of torture to create public opinion against torture, reject it and deter the authority to compel with international agreements. 3.Organize national campaign to resist the torture and ratify the optional protocol and amend the constitution and the penal code and Criminal procedure to suit with international conventions in Yemen. 4.Provide health, psychological and legal services to victims of torture.</narrative>
  </description>
